{"thag2.29:0.1":"Theragatha 2.29 ","thag2.29:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.29:0.3":"Tatiyavagga ","thag2.29:0.4":"Bharadvajattheragatha ","thag2.29:1.1":"“Nadanti evam sappanna, ","thag2.29:1.2":"sihava girigabbhare; ","thag2.29:1.3":"Vira vijitasangama, ","thag2.29:1.4":"jetva maram savahinim. ","thag2.29:2.1":"Sattha ca paricinno me, ","thag2.29:2.2":"dhammo sangho ca pujito; ","thag2.29:2.3":"Ahanca vitto sumano, ","thag2.29:2.4":"puttam disva anasavan”ti. ","thag2.29:2.5":"… Bharadvajo thero …. "}